# Build-time settings for the web app.
# Copy to `.env`. The dev server proxies `/api` to localhost:8787 (see vite.config.ts),
# so this only matters if you point the build at a non-default API host.

# VITE_API_URL is currently unused by the web app — axios talks to /api and is proxied.
# Reserved for future production builds that bypass the proxy.
